venue.name: Saint Anselm College - New Hampshire Institute of Politics

item.description:
"Coming to Terms with the Rulemaking Power of the Judicial Branch
and its Impact on Personal Liberty."What did the citizens of New Hampshire understand they were approving when they voted to ratify Article 73-a, Part II of the New Hampshire Constitution... versus... what they actually got?

Your Emcee: Garrett Lear - New Hampshire's Patriot Pastor
And featuring the Honorable...
Dan Itse
Paul Mirski
Gregory Sorg
Paul Ingbretson
Suggested Donation: $15.00
Light supper to be provided

Pre-registration is required here: http://nhccs.org/2012%20Seminar_Registration.htm
